---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<Layout metadata={{ title: 'Our Story - Aspire College Gamber' }}>

  <!-- Banner Section -->
  <section id="story-banner" class="banner">
    <div class="floating-icons">
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:school" width="50" color="#ffffffcc"></iconify-icon>
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:book-open-variant" width="50" color="#facc15"></iconify-icon>
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:lightbulb-on-outline" width="50" color="#60a5fa"></iconify-icon>
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:pen" width="50" color="#f472b6"></iconify-icon>
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:graduation-cap" width="50" color="#ffffffb3"></iconify-icon>
    </div>

    <div class="banner-content">
      <h1>Our Story</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">A legacy of education, opportunity, and community transformation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scroll-indicator" onclick="document.getElementById('story-text').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })">
      <span class="scroll-dot"></span>
      <span class="scroll-line"></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section id="story-text" class="story-section">
    <div class="floating-icons">
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:school" width="40" color="#ffffff99"></iconify-icon>
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:notebook-outline" width="40" color="#34d399"></iconify-icon>
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:chalkboard-teacher" width="40" color="#fbbf24"></iconify-icon>
      <iconify-icon icon="mdi:book-education" width="40" color="#c084fc"></iconify-icon>
    </div>

    <div class="story-content">
      <p>Nearly a decade ago, Mohammed Bhuttor began his journey in Gambar, a place deeply connected to his family’s legacy. He built homes, raised animals, and cultivated the land, cherishing its rich heritage. But as he looked around, he saw something missing—opportunity, especially for young minds eager to learn.</p>

      <p>Determined to change that, he started with a simple idea: an elementary school that removed all barriers to education. No uniforms, no books to buy—everything provided. His goal was to make learning accessible to every child, particularly girls, who often had fewer opportunities. This wasn’t just a school; it was a lasting initiative to uplift the community.</p>

      <p>His passion for education was contagious. His son, Zulfiqar Ali Bhuttor, saw the impact and joined him in this mission. Together, they expanded the vision beyond just primary education. They knew that students needed more than just classrooms— they needed skills, guidance, and opportunities to build successful futures. With this ambition, they founded Aspire College Gamber, creating a space where students could pursue higher education in a supportive and enriching environment.</p>

      <p>Education, however, is more than just academics. Recognizing the importance of a well-rounded student life, they introduced facilities beyond classrooms— a gym, a swimming pool, and even an affordable pizza spot near campus, ensuring students have access to both quality education and a balanced lifestyle.</p>

      <p>Today, their efforts continue, fueled by a dedicated team of highly trained faculty and a shared commitment to empowering the youth of Gambar. What started as one man’s dream has grown into a thriving institution shaping the future of countless students— and this is only the beginning.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Banner and Story Styling */
    .banner, .story-section {
      background-color: #0c1a2a;
      color: #f0f0f0;
    }

    .banner {
      height: 90vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .banner-content h1 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #facc15;
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    .scroll-indicator {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 30px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .scroll-dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      background: #facc15;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .scroll-line {
      width: 2px;
      height: 24px;
      background: #facc15;
    }

    .story-section {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 2;
      position: relative;
    }

    .story-content {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .story-content p {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    /* Floating Icons Styling */
    .floating-icons {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .floating-icons iconify-icon {
      position: absolute;
      opacity: 0.25;
    }

    .banner .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(1) { top: 12%; left: 10%; }
    .banner .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(2) { top: 22%; right: 8%; }
    .banner .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(3) { bottom: 18%; left: 20%; }
    .banner .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(4) { top: 65%; right: 12%; }
    .banner .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(5) { bottom: 8%; left: 45%; }

    .story-section .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(1) { top: 10%; left: 75%; }
    .story-section .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(2) { top: 30%; left: 10%; }
    .story-section .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(3) { top: 60%; right: 15%; }
    .story-section .floating-icons iconify-icon:nth-child(4) { bottom: 10%; left: 35%; }
  </style>

  <script src="https://code.iconify.design/iconify-icon/1.0.7/iconify-icon.min.js" client:load></script>
</Layout>
